---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
    title={"About Nooze – The Story Behind the Smart Alarm App"}
    description={"Learn about Nooze, the smart alarm app born from a personal struggle with poor sleep. Meet the developer and the mission to make mornings better."}
    keywords={"about nooze, nooze alarm story, smart alarm developer, sleep app mission, indie alarm app"}
    canonical={"about.html"}
    ogTitle={"About Nooze - Our Story & Mission"}
    ogDescription={"Born from personal struggle with poor sleep. Meet the developer behind Nooze."}
    active={"about"}
>

  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://noozealarm.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"About\",\"item\":\"https://noozealarm.com/about.html\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>

<main class="flex-1 pt-16">
        <!-- Hero -->
        <section class="hero-bg pt-32 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="aurora"></div>
            <div class="holo-grid tilt-grid"></div>
            <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
            <div class="orb orb-3"></div>
            <div class="scanlines"></div>
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
                <span class="holo-chip mb-6 reveal"><span class="dot"></span> Built solo, with care</span>
                <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4 reveal delay-1 tracking-tight">
                    Our <span class="iris-text">Story</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto reveal delay-2">A personal struggle with sleep became a mission: build the alarm clock you actually want to wake up to.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-divider"></div>

        <!-- Mission -->
        <section class="py-20">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="holo-card reveal"><div class="holo-card-inner" style="padding:40px;">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The <span class="gradient-text-cyan">Mission</span></h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Mornings shouldn't be a struggle. For millions of people, the alarm is the worst part of the day &mdash; a jarring sound that rips them from deep sleep and leaves them groggy.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Nooze exists to fix that. Smart wake timing during your lightest sleep phase, seven wake challenges instead of a snooze button, and a gamified streak system that makes you actually look forward to mornings.</p>
                </div></div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-10">
                    <div class="metric reveal delay-1"><div class="num"><span data-counter="0" data-duration="1000">0</span><span class="unit">%</span></div><div class="lbl">Snooze Button</div><div class="desc">Replaced with wake challenges.</div></div>
                    <div class="metric reveal delay-2"><div class="num"><span data-counter="8" data-duration="1200">0</span></div><div class="lbl">Wake Challenges</div><div class="desc">Math, photo, QR &amp; more.</div></div>
                    <div class="metric reveal delay-3"><div class="num"><span data-counter="4" data-duration="1300">0</span></div><div class="lbl">Sleep Phases</div><div class="desc">Awake · Light · Deep · REM</div></div>
                    <div class="metric reveal delay-1"><div class="num"><span data-counter="100" data-duration="1500">0</span><span class="unit">%</span></div><div class="lbl">On-Device</div><div class="desc">Biometrics never leave your phone.</div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-divider"></div>

        <!-- Origin Story -->
        <section class="py-20">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="reveal">
                    <span class="holo-chip mb-4"><span class="dot"></span> The origin</span>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">How It <span class="gradient-text">Started</span></h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>Nooze was born from personal experience with restless sleep. Traditional alarms only made it worse &mdash; getting yanked out of deep sleep left me more exhausted than when I went to bed.</p>
                        <p>The first insight was simple: <span class="text-white">what if the alarm understood your sleep cycle and waited until you were already in light sleep?</span></p>
                        <p>The second was about behaviour. Snoozing fragments your sleep and trains you to dread mornings. Removing the snooze button entirely &mdash; and making the dismissal a tiny challenge instead &mdash; turns wake-up into something you actually finish.</p>
                        <p>The third was about repetition. Most habits stick when there's feedback. So Nooze tracks streaks, awards XP, unlocks achievements and lets you duel friends. The morning becomes a win, not a chore.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-divider"></div>

        <!-- Developer -->
        <section class="py-20">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="holo-card reveal"><div class="holo-card-inner" style="padding:40px;">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <img src="assets/snimka.jpg" alt="Teodor Mirchev, Nooze developer" width="160" height="160" class="w-40 h-40 rounded-2xl object-cover border border-primary/30 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(0,188,212,0.25)]" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="holo-chip mb-3"><span class="dot"></span> Founder &amp; Developer</span>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">Teodor Mirchev</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3 mt-3">Built Nooze end-to-end &mdash; the alarm engine, sleep detection, gamification, the lot. The app you'll install is the work of one person obsessed with making mornings better.</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
                            <a href="mailto:noozesupport@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline text-sm">noozesupport@gmail.com</a>
                            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/teodor-mirchev-91115a305" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-gray-400 hover:text-primary text-sm transition-colors">
                                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
                                LinkedIn
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </div></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-divider"></div>

        <!-- Values -->
        <section class="py-20">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-10 text-center reveal">What We <span class="gradient-text">Stand For</span></h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="holo-card tilt reveal delay-1"><div class="holo-card-inner tilt-inner">
                        <div class="feature-icon mb-4">
                            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Privacy First</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Local data is encrypted at rest. Sleep biometrics never leave your device. Cloud sync is opt-in and minimal &mdash; alarms, gamification, friends only.</p>
                    </div></div>
                    <div class="holo-card tilt reveal delay-2"><div class="holo-card-inner tilt-inner">
                        <div class="feature-icon mb-4">
                            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">User-Centric</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">No dark patterns, no upsell pop-ups. Every feature has to earn its keep. Premium is &euro;2.99/month and unlocks polish, not basic functionality.</p>
                    </div></div>
                    <div class="holo-card tilt reveal delay-3"><div class="holo-card-inner tilt-inner">
                        <div class="feature-icon mb-4">
                            <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Science-Based</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Smart wake builds on sleep-cycle research, not vibes. Detection fuses motion, sound and wearable data with confidence weighting and graceful fallbacks.</p>
                    </div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-divider"></div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <section class="py-28 relative hero-bg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="aurora"></div>
            <div class="holo-grid tilt-grid" style="opacity:0.7;"></div>
            <div class="orb orb-2" style="opacity:0.2;"></div>
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
                <div class="holo-card reveal"><div class="holo-card-inner text-center" style="padding:48px 32px;">
                    <span class="launch-stamp mb-6"><span class="dot"></span> Live on Google Play</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Nooze Alarm is Finally Here</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">Years of late nights, sleep science, and stubborn engineering &mdash; now in your pocket. Install it, then check the roadmap to see what's coming next.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-4">
                        <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nooze.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="play-badge" aria-label="Get Nooze on Google Play">
                            <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ffffff"><path d="M3.6 1.6c-.3.3-.5.8-.5 1.4v18c0 .6.2 1.1.5 1.4l.1.1L13.8 12 3.7 1.6l-.1.1zM17.4 8.4l-3-1.7L5.3 1.2c-.4-.2-.8-.2-1.1 0l11.4 11.4 1.8-1.8c1-.6 1-1.8 0-2.4zM4.2 22.8c.3.2.7.2 1.1 0l9.1-5.5 3-1.7-2.2-2.2L4.2 22.8z"/></svg></span>
                            <span class="stack"><span class="small">Get it on</span><span class="big">Google Play</span></span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="roadmap.html" class="btn-outline"><span>View Roadmap</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div></div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>
